Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:83100,87780}COLIN'S LOVE AND THE TREASURE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89040,90220}{\i1}I'm leaving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90360,91800}{\i1}Be careful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93050,94040}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99020,100300}Thank you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100450,104570}You thought I forgot my bag and I was on\Nmy way to school, so you brought it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105570,108310}But I don't need a bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.47,0:01:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108470,110910}Today we will go for a stroll outside the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111510,113590}Look, this is for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114590,118120}So I don't want you to go to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125350,127150}Do you want to go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132650,134180}Everyone is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134320,135780}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135950,137090}You understand, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137180,138820}You have to wait until we move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138920,139980}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141760,142970}Hello John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143090,145270}Will Lassie be released today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145370,146900}Yes that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147000,149530}Because they went to the cart regularly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149630,150610}- Yes!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151740,153730}You seem to have difficulty in your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153820,157370}The teacher ended up going in a school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157530,159620}But I am very excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161700,164300}Everything is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166680,167560}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169900,171890}Everyone, we will move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172020,175420}Take care not to fall from the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175450,176680}{\i1}- Yes!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176890,179050}{\i1}- Now, please!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185760,188560}Come on! Come! Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191780,193170}In here! In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200640,202350}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204200,206540}Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234870,237990}All of you, get off of the cart\Nand then board on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238110,240050}I go first to the reception!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240710,241760}We'll go get the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243030,243880}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244170,245480}Come on! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245500,246580}Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250400,251700}Uncle, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251720,252930}We depend on you to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252930,255810}Yes, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258630,260160}No, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261520,262310}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262390,263320}- Oh!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264040,265020}- Uh!\N- Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288550,291100}We are on board now, but what next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291180,293720}Where can I hide Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293990,296070}John, it's the teacher Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296250,296920}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297010,298850}Colin, I rely on you to take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301140,302170}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302350,304560}What's the matter, John Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304580,306570}Sorry, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307350,309140}{\i1}I have a question!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309160,309890}{\i1}Uh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310360,312740}I must hide Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320080,320930}Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324890,326250}This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326400,326990}Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327010,329930}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332750,333160}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333190,334470}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339250,340870}Thank you, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341150,342520}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342640,343860}Hey!  You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344160,344860}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345180,345910}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346830,347930}My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350820,353890}Damn, it was my hat that I loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353910,355500}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359280,361260}We can't recover it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361380,362530}I will forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367670,369700}Right, I have to hide Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369720,370950}- Hide?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372170,373860}I know a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373880,374450}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375410,376260}{\i1}I see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376340,378920}{\i1}I'm also going to the same place, Skull Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379200,381490}T-t-the same place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381790,387490}But when we return I'll go to a different\Nship, which is bound for Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387740,390840}My father went before me\Nand now he is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391200,392570}You are a foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392680,395160}I wanted to see one of you already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400440,401890}Tell me, what is the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402010,403090}It's Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403110,405100}Wrong, I mean your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405120,405700}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405920,406650}Uh... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406740,407660}Co-Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407970,409340}I'm Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409480,410740}Nice to meet you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412200,413710}Nice to meet you, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414300,416000}Nice to meet you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419260,421350}- Uh... uh...\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421870,424460}A-a little while ago... What was that paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424580,426530}It seemed important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426640,427780}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428080,429710}A treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429800,431130}A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435650,440120}When I get to Skull Island\NI'll look for a treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440630,442570}C-can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443080,445620}Y-you can consider that instead\Nof the hat you lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446280,448120}Lassie, do you want to go with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458260,459650}Colin Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460980,463760}Does anyone know where Colin Jones is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464250,466660}Maybe we should search the ship again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467280,468250}It's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468330,469700}He can't get out just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469800,471910}This is because he's alone with with Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471940,472550}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472830,475400}Could it have fallen into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475510,476210}Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477320,478290}Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479130,480400}Colin! Las--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481180,484050}You brought Lassie with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484290,485900}No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486110,487610}Teacher, I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487730,489030}I will answer later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490280,492540}Teacher, I apologize for the delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492540,493940}{\i1}Colin, what about the dog?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495010,496780}What do you want from Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497160,498110}Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498370,500030}Is this dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500230,501010}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501280,503530}Say "Hello", Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504650,505490}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505800,507060}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507090,507960}I'm Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507980,510100}We have become friends on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510120,511570}Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512350,516010}Now get ready, we will eat\Nour lunch in the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516180,517600}{\i1}Now, let's move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517730,519030}{\i1}- Yes!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520770,522560}What does that mean, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523640,525880}Hello John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526020,526690}- Hm?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526880,528840}I'm Chris, nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528960,530970}Colin told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531240,533600}It was a good plan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533730,534380}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534480,536040}Hello, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536220,540480}When we have a vacuum, you need\Nto take care of the Lassie thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540540,541060}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541090,542650}That would be a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542790,545050}I will wait for you in that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545100,545680}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545800,547290}I rely on you to take care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547420,549450}Let's go, Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550440,551500}Ah, a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552200,553180}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554010,555370}It's Lassie's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556100,557080}I understand, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557300,559030}We'll meet later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559830,561700}- Farewell, Chris!\N- No... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561770,562850}As I thougt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562880,564740}Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564770,565510}- Oh!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568550,570720}When it heard its name it didn't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570720,572780}Maybe it's really another dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572940,574000}- Ah...\N- Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579300,581600}It's nice to listen to the sea, Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581600,582880}I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582910,583760}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583780,586390}Treasure hunt... This is very exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587040,588820}Is it on that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588820,591350}It's an island but we can walk on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591450,592490}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592740,594820}In leisure time to look for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594840,595980}Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596430,597150}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597340,598230}Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598510,599620}Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599790,603440}You can go down to the white sandy beach\Nin the afternoon when it's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603610,605540}Don't go far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605620,608990}Also don't go on that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609170,610040}{\i1}You understand?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610070,611300}{\i1}- Yes!\N- Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611890,613700}We can't go to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613800,614930}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615120,615900}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623400,624140}Were you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624160,624960}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625070,627300}- And this will restore Lassie to you!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628170,628920}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629340,631940}I have to go with Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631970,632470}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632510,633830}But the teacher said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634330,636750}Colin, I don't want to force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636770,638040}I can go by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638040,639280}No, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639690,641670}I want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642570,643610}A-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643720,645420}Is that so, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645620,646910}I will go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646940,647910}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647940,649410}Ah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649440,650740}It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650740,652900}Colin, you can go on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653280,653930}E-eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653970,655120}Alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656470,660340}Sorry, I wanted to take Lassie with us but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661290,662360}It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662420,664280}W-what is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664280,665370}Sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665370,666540}Come on, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666970,669820}I'll borrow Lassie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669840,670600}{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678060,678940}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678980,681430}Lassie follows them too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681650,684190}Listen, why can't I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684220,686860}John, it's too boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686930,687920}Boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688060,689240}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690100,690880}Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690910,692170}Love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692200,693340}What does Colin mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693570,694880}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695080,696350}Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713970,716320}{\i1}Listen, how does the treasure look?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716450,720130}Could you have seen two hackers before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720300,721330}Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721410,723070}It's a little trifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723150,725520}In the eyes of people is worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725740,728680}But for me it's my precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729260,730540}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730660,733740}It isn't a pirate treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734010,734990}What do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735020,735840}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735930,740270}Not so, but I knew nothing\Nabout the treasure at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743590,744280}- Huh?\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744380,745090}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745330,748000}Wait! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754180,756560}I want to look for treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756600,757860}But Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758060,760530}Do you really love Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760640,762260}I think he doesn't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762700,763310}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763570,765140}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765140,766810}I was just xxx!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766890,768080}John the insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768410,769210}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769210,771730}Do you know anything about the age of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771760,774010}Damn, I'm not insensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774030,774910}- Oh!\N- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774980,776140}Just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776140,778860}Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784210,785660}{\i1}We have climbed a lot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786480,788830}Chris, is this really the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789050,792220}Yes, if we walk this way we will\Nreach the top of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792540,793160}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793300,795190}Up to the peak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796910,797810}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798480,800390}Are you fine? You're tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800470,802100}I-I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802380,803670}That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804010,804580}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807170,808890}{\i1}It's pushing hard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814490,815840}{\i1}John Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817660,818920}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819260,820830}I have a question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821050,822480}Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824860,825940}- Uh...\N- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830660,831680}This...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831680,833420}It's a landslide...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833860,835030}I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835600,837770}Although we have had all\Nthe trouble to get here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840180,840990}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846390,848100}Lassie does it perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848180,849370}Let's go through there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849490,852740}Look, Lassie walks the natural way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853440,856070}But we can't climb like Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856210,857530}Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857890,859680}I'll make holes for climbing, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859910,861300}Ah? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861710,863610}I'll start digging!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863730,865740}So stay away and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865830,866430}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889760,891600}Now climb up, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891620,892100}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895450,896950}Don't look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897100,899500}Yes, you can fix your feet this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899600,900240}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906070,908070}We have already reached the peak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908130,908760}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908860,909930}And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910080,911630}Listen, show me the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911650,912210}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.48,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912480,913140}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914460,915680}A compass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915850,917560}It looks like a real treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917690,920980}But it doesn't help as long\Nas we don't have a map!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921120,922380}Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922480,924850}Thay way is the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925020,927610}So I think the treasure is to the northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928070,929210}Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930820,932070}What do you see to see there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933760,934970}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935270,937820}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943360,944510}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945540,946230}- Hm?\N- Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946480,947480}- Ah...!\N- Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948070,950080}{\i1}The road has disappeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951660,954630}The sea was sunk by the tidal wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955180,956310}Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956340,958080}Someone help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958100,960340}The road has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962750,964560}They can't hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965760,968210}This is not the time to search for treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968780,971050}{\i1}We have to think about the way back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972310,974070}Colin, can you swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974270,976790}I can't swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977610,979310}Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980770,983900}In the meantime, John and\NSandy will notice that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984100,988240}If they don't notice quickly, the ship\Nbound for Australia will be departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989130,991570}Me too, maybe I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991830,993800}Anyway, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995230,998910}{\i1}I don't mind not going to Australia...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999020,999900}Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000960,1004980}The treasure was a memory of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005330,1006380}A memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006820,1009910}{\i1}My mother died last month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010000,1010620}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012380,1016220}My father remembered when\Nthey lived in the same house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016390,1019720}He therefore decided to live\Nin a foreign country to build a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020430,1023440}I really want to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023940,1026020}But I can't say that to my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026160,1027070}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027510,1030450}So before leaving England
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030550,1033970}I decided to look for my mother's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034910,1040570}{\i1}When I was small, my father, my mother\Nand me came here to play a treasure game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041230,1042470}{\i1}It was fun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043060,1046900}The map is from my mom\Nthat's why I care about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048280,1049910}After all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050640,1052630}I haven't found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056560,1058630}Let's go and find it... Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059170,1059800}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059820,1062650}You can't leave without your precious treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062650,1065510}But we have to think about the return!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065510,1067200}I-I'll find a solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067650,1069740}So let 's go, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071440,1072180}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083490,1085320}North West! North West!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085320,1087140}Chris, is it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087140,1089120}Yeah, no mistake on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092940,1093660}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094330,1095330}{\i1}It's there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095330,1097260}{\i1}It was buried under that tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097500,1099030}You're not wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099110,1100970}When I was little I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101070,1102880}- We've found it!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104280,1105010}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105060,1108290}My mother planted the seed,\Nit has already grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108430,1109640}And now let's dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109810,1110360}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119350,1120460}- Ah...!\N- Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124790,1126670}{\i1}Ah! Beautiful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127200,1129540}My mother wanted to see\Nhim with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130450,1131950}It seems to have something written!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132400,1133560}Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134650,1136210}{\i1}Dear Chris,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136380,1141460}{\i1}When you read this you should\Nbe grown up and be a good girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148730,1149740}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155720,1158190}I have to go to Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158340,1160310}If my father doesn't see me,\NI'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163490,1164160}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166070,1167120}Let's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172640,1175260}Even if it slips from me, I won't sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175290,1176930}I will swim and call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177060,1178790}At this time, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179280,1181030}I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181200,1183580}It's not good to go both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183850,1185720}So we won't be able to help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185880,1186490}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186830,1188990}I'll be fine, leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189260,1190580}Colin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192910,1194460}Do your best, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195410,1197200}Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197900,1198610}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198950,1202560}If delayed, the ship bound\Nfor Australia will be departed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203010,1204240}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205270,1207260}Stop it, Colin Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207260,1208900}Go back to the ground quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208990,1210950}Turn! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211100,1212180}We will help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212400,1212950}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212980,1214290}We survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214320,1217100}xxx
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218200,1221750}The ship bound for Australia\Nwill leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222130,1223270}Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223290,1224300}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225300,1226950}She seems to have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227110,1228560}You have to say farewell now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228680,1229730}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231490,1233220}Chris, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233350,1234660}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234900,1236440}You go to Australia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236600,1241130}Thanks to you, Colin, I found\Nthe most precious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241270,1242380}Thank you, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243750,1244340}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244560,1245680}- Ah...!\N- Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247830,1249180}Thank you, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252260,1254220}Goodbye, John! Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254350,1255540}Goodbye, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255720,1256930}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258290,1260230}Goodbye... Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264400,1266250}Chris! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266270,1269800}Colin, I'll never forget\Nwhat happened this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269830,1272320}Me too! Me too!\NI'll never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272360,1274870}Goodbye! Goodbye, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275500,1277770}Goodbye... Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278940,1280680}Chris has already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280770,1284260}Listen, did you find the treasure?\NWhat was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284790,1285860}I'm sorry, John...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286620,1287720}{\i1}It's a secret!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288560,1290350}{\i1}It's only for two people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293030,1293970}Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294430,1295830}Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296180,1298270}And now everyone, get ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298500,1300190}Woe to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301310,1305180}{\i1}We have to go back because\Nit's waiting for us now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319360,1322080}{\i1}Has the influenza epidemic\Nspread in the village?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322210,1324290}{\i1}Even my father got sick and stayed at home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324490,1325850}{\i1}And daily visit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325920,1328230}{\i1}are very tiring for my mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328320,1329700}{\i1}Is she okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330400,1333690}{\i1}Next episode:\NIT IS SERIOUS! MY MOTHER FELL{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333880,1335220}{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
